{"title":"石子篇","authors":["张雪杉"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":1,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"石子篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张雪杉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一粒小小的石子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诞生在巍巍太行的怀抱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车把我带进城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放在这建筑工地的一角。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要和钢筋、水泥结为一体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同把雄伟的大厦建造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我离开巍巍的太行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中曾感到阵阵悲凉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我被送进建筑工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中曾感到阵阵凄惶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我被筑进这坚实的地基，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"混身感到有无比的力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕山、太行，数百里峻岭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恒山、贺兰，数百里奇峰……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从东海之滨到西北边陲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州有多少父老弟兄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他们用自己的钢铁之躯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起了中华民族的万里长城！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}